<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Nightcrawler Mod</title>

<style>

body{
background:#000;
color:#FFB000;
font-family:Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif;
margin:0;
padding:0;
text-align:center;
}

.container{
width:560px;
margin:auto;
padding:10px;
}

.banner img{
width:520px;
height:140px;
border:2px solid #333;
margin-bottom:10px;
}

h1{
font-size:28px;
margin:5px 0 15px 0;
animation:glow 2s infinite alternate;
}

@keyframes glow{
from{
color:#FF4444;
text-shadow:0 0 5px #FF0000,0 0 15px #FF0000;
}
to{
color:#FFD700;
text-shadow:0 0 10px #FFD700,0 0 25px #FFD700;
}
}

.panel{
background:#111;
border:1px solid #333;
padding:12px;
margin-top:10px;
text-align:left;
}

.panel h2{
color:#FFA500;
margin-top:0;
}

.command{
margin-bottom:3px;
}

.footer{
margin-top:15px;
padding:10px;
border-top:1px solid #333;
font-size:13px;
color:#AAA;
}

.serverbox{
background:#0a0a0a;
border:1px solid #444;
padding:8px;
margin-top:10px;
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<div class="banner">
<img src="https://i.imgur.com/7vzAMvu.jpeg">
</div>

<h1>[NC] Nightcrawler Mod</h1>

<div class="panel">

<h2>Welcome</h2>

Humans must survive and eliminate the <b>Nightcrawlers</b> while Nightcrawlers hunt silently in the darkness.<br><br>

<b>Game Overview</b><br>
Humans rely on teamwork, equipment, and special items to survive.<br>
Nightcrawlers rely on stealth, mobility, and surprise attacks.

</div>

<div class="panel">

<h2>Server Rules</h2>

* No cheating or scripting advantages<br>
* No exploiting map or game bugs<br>
* Respect players and admins<br>
* No spam or microphone abuse<br>
* No harassment or toxic behavior<br>
* Play the objective and support teammates<br>
* Follow admin instructions<br>

</div>

<div class="panel">

<h2>Commands</h2>

<div class="command"><b>/menu</b> - Open item menu</div>
<div class="command"><b>/guns</b> - Select your weapons</div>
<div class="command"><b>/help</b> - View gameplay help</div>
<div class="command"><b>F</b> - Use your special item</div>
<div class="command"><b>+sprint</b> - Activate stamina</div>
<div class="command"><b>+tmine</b> - Plant tripmine</div>
<div class="command"><b>+pickupmine</b> - Pick up mines</div>

</div>

<div class="panel">

<h2>Human Tips</h2>

* Stay together and watch each other's backs<br>
* Use sonar scans to detect Nightcrawlers<br>
* Secure chokepoints with mines<br>
* Protect teammates and avoid isolation

</div>

<div class="panel">

<h2>Nightcrawler Tips</h2>

* Stay hidden and strike from darkness<br>
* Use teleport to ambush humans<br>
* Climb walls for unexpected angles<br>
* Target isolated players first

</div>

<div class="serverbox">

<b>Server Information</b><br><br>

IP: <b>YOUR_SERVER_IP</b><br>
Discord: <b>discord.gg/YOURDISCORD</b>

</div>

<div class="footer">

Good luck. The hunt has begun.

</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
